    "en": "## Visual Stimulus Response\r\n\r\nThe following page is an example of the Visual Stimulus Response widget. This complex widget shows the user a certain number of trials. In each trial the user is presented with a visual stimulus in the center of the screen. The user must respond to the stimuli by pressing a button at the bottom of the screen.\r\n\r\nThis widget is highly configurable. You can configure the sampling method and sampling size, whether to show the user feedback, and much more.\r\n\r\nThe following page contains a little Jeopardy! quiz."
